	Bulldog Beckham    
	 London, Dec. 28 (PTI): David Beckhams Christmas celebrations got a bit posh after wife Victoria bought him an expensive bulldog.       
	Victoria, who is also known as Posh Spice, bought the dog from a local breeder after her footballer husband spoke of Englands bulldog spirit in the run-up to next years World Cup campaign, reports The Sun .      
	David absolutely loves the bulldog. Posh said she chose the breed because it is a symbol of Beckss spirit on the football field, a source said.     
	Calm Alec    
	London (PTI): Actor Alec Baldwin fears he will have to calm his nerves while hosting the Oscars next year because his co-host Steve Martin is fragile under pressure. The actor was hoping Martins experience as a comedian would help him overcome his stage terror before the big awards show in March. But Baldwin thinks Martin is already a wreck. I called up Steve and said: Do you think we should do this? And he said: Of course we shouldnt do it! He said: Wed be fools to do it, and thats exactly why were going to do it  to prove everyone wrong, he explained.     
	Pink habit    
	Los Angeles (PTI): Popstar Pink has asked her friends and family members to ration the cigarettes she smokes in a desperate attempt to cut back on the habit. She has already stopped smoking at home and now wants to limit the amount of cigarettes she puffs on while going out with friends.    
	Untidy star    
	New York (PTI): Actress Charlize Theron is best known for making polished red carpet appearances. However, the actress looked haggard as she went shopping on Christmas Day. The actress looked glum as she went shopping with her mother without a scrap of makeup on her face and her hair tied up in an untidy pony tail.
                                                                                                                                                      
